Package pagerank.datastructure.graph

Class AdjacencyMatrix<T>

java.lang.Object
pagerank.datastructure.graph.AdjacencyMatrix<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the vertices in the graph
All Implemented Interfaces:
Graph<T>
public class AdjacencyMatrix<T> extends Object implements Graph<T>
AdjacencyMatrix implementation of the Graph interface. This implementation represents the graph as an adjacency matrix.
